          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bbsam123/" class=" " title="Ryan Tam">Ryan Tam</a>
                (克己慎独)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12350785">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">然而有时思想之禁抑不必皆来自高压，一片乐观之声无形中也删略了不那么如意的消息。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-04-14 00:19</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>然而有时思想之禁抑不必皆来自高压，一片乐观之声无形中也删略了不那么如意的消息。</q></blockquote>
